<task id="042" project="ai-json-prompt-schema-system">
  <metadata>
    <title>Implement promptSchemaOverride Merge with Directives</title>
    <phase>5</phase>
    <tags>bff-api, api, implement</tags>
    <estimate>2h</estimate>
    <dependencies>002</dependencies>
    <parallel-group>B</parallel-group>
  </metadata>

  <prompt>
    <goal>Implement the override merge logic that allows node-level customization of base Action schemas with directive support.</goal>
    <context>
      A reusable Action scope (e.g., "General Document Analysis") can be customized per-node via
      promptSchemaOverride in sprk_configjson. The merge rules:
      - Default: constraint arrays concatenate (base + override)
      - Default: output.fields arrays concatenate (override appends to base)
      - Directive: __replace: true on a section replaces instead of merging
      - Scalar fields (role, task) replace if present in override
      The merged result is what the renderer processes.
    </context>
    <constraints>
      - Create PromptSchemaOverrideMerger as a separate utility class
      - Default merge: concatenate arrays (constraints, output.fields)
      - __replace directive: fully replace the section
      - Scalar replacement: role, task, context replace if present
      - Merge happens before rendering (renderer receives merged schema)
      - Unit testable as pure function
    </constraints>
  </prompt>

  <knowledge>
    <files>
      <file>projects/ai-json-prompt-schema-system/design.md</file>
      <file>projects/ai-json-prompt-schema-system/spec.md</file>
      <file>.claude/constraints/ai.md</file>
    </files>
  </knowledge>

  <steps>
    <step order="1">Read design.md "Node-Level Override" section for merge rules</step>
    <step order="2">Create PromptSchemaOverrideMerger.cs with:
      - Merge(baseSchema: PromptSchema, override: PromptSchema?) → PromptSchema
      - Array concatenation for constraints and output.fields by default
      - __replace detection and full replacement logic
      - Scalar field replacement for role, task, context</step>
    <step order="3">Integrate into AiAnalysisNodeExecutor: read promptSchemaOverride from configJson, merge before rendering</step>
    <step order="4">Verify build: `dotnet build src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/`</step>
  </steps>

  <tools>
    <tool>Read</tool>
    <tool>Write</tool>
    <tool>Edit</tool>
    <tool>Bash(dotnet build)</tool>
  </tools>

  <outputs>
    <output>src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/PromptSchemaOverrideMerger.cs (new)</output>
    <output>src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Nodes/AiAnalysisNodeExecutor.cs (modified)</output>
  </outputs>

  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion>Array fields concatenate by default</criterion>
    <criterion>__replace directive fully replaces section</criterion>
    <criterion>Scalar fields replace when present in override</criterion>
    <criterion>Null override returns base schema unchanged</criterion>
    <criterion>Project builds without errors</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>
</task>
